models.common.workers

Class PersonalSingleWorker

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.common.workers.Worker
      • models.common.workers.PersonalSingleWorker

  • @Entity
public class PersonalSingleWorker
extends Worker
    DB entity of the concrete Worker if a study is run as Personal Single Worker. This kind of worker is for an external run. The worker can run the study only once. The worker is created by a JATOS user before the study is started.
